metadata.description:
Hey friends :) this week i'm dropping The Eternal Garden Master Collection, my first-ever artist/producer sample pack hosted by Arpeggi's new platform, Kits. It features every vocal & instrument from Eternal Garden and I'm honored to share it with you all. 

Kits Season 1 features sample packs from top artists building in web3 â€” TK, MSFT, Dot, Ramzoid, Edwin, & AbJo.

In this track, billings chops, reworks, and processes every sample from the Kits Season 1 Preview Pack into a single track that showcases the quality and versatility of the artist sample packs to come. I heard this track and immediately wanted to mint it to Sound. As the first artist on Season One, I'm happy to lead the way bring this experiment to you all. 

6 artists, 13 Samples, Open Edition.

Read more at: kits.io/

Artwork: Kits Team
